----- stdout -----
TUI for managing NixOS Artifacts

Usage: artifacts [OPTIONS] [FLAKE]

Arguments:
  [FLAKE]  Path to flake directory (default: current directory)

Options:
      --machine <MACHINE>      Filter by machine name (repeatable)
      --home <HOME>            Filter by home-manager user (repeatable)
      --artifact <ARTIFACT>    Filter by artifact name (repeatable)
      --log-level <LOG_LEVEL>  Set the logging level [default: info] [possible values: error, warning, info, debug, trace]
      --no-emoji               Disable emoji output
  -h, --help                   Print help
  -V, --version                Print version

